Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.80,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}總是惹怒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:07.72,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}那樣纖細的指尖
